channel.description: Join me as I share with my friends the kind of fun facts, stories, and history I would talk about if we were stuck in line at a theme park together!

item.author: Julia Warner
item.itunes:author: Julia Warner
item.title: Figment Lives!
item.description: In this, our very first episode, Julia and Jin discuss the turbulant history of everyone's favorite Epcot attraction: Journey Into Imagination With Figment! We discuss all three incarnations of the ride and dutifully try our best to honor Figment as the cultural and religious icon that he is.

item.author: Julia Warner
item.itunes:author: Julia Warner
item.title: Space Mountain's Identity Crisis
item.description: Julia is joined by her Mom and sister in this episode exploring the multiple themed overlays applied to the multiple Space Mountains across the globe and throughout history. Tune in to hear all about scary nebula ghosts, canonical Star Wars battles, and how much teens love the Red Hot Chili Peppers!

item.author: Julia Warner
item.itunes:author: Julia Warner
item.title: Maelstrom v. Frozen
item.description: Julia is joined by her friend Stephanie in this episode in honor of the late, great Maelstrom! May it rest in peace after being replaced by Frozen: Ever After! Tune in to hear all about very authentic Norwegian culture, how the two rides are similar, and whether or not Stephanie wants the three headed troll to be her boyfriend!
